OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHuge need for foster carers
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin Wales, say councils     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, There is a massive need for more foster
OL,6, carers in Wales, say local authority   
OL,7, foster services.                       
OL,9,FFoster Wales, the network representing 
OL,10,Ffostering teams, said there were more  
OL,11,Fthan 7,000 children in the care system,
OL,12,Fbut only 3,800 foster families.        
OL,14,FThe group said it wanted to tackle     
OL,15,F"misconceptions" to reach a target of  
OL,16,Frecruiting 800 foster households over  
OL,17,Fthe next two years.                    
OL,19,FThe Welsh government said it was       
OL,20,Fcommitted to increasing the number.    
